    "comment": "Muy básico el servicio. Pocos alimentos. Mantenimientos regular. Aparentemente el surtidor marca de mas\n\n(Translated by Google)\nThe service is very basic. There\u0027s a limited food selection. Maintenance is inconsistent. Apparently, the pump is overfilling.",
